# =============================================================================
# 🌐 GFW-bypass Proxy · 中国大陆开发机 REQUIRED
# =============================================================================
# 本项目开发机位于中国大陆，默认通往 github.com:443 的路由会被 GFW 重置
# (典型症状:  / )。
# 必须先配置 HTTP/HTTPS 代理后才能 git push / pull / Supabase CLI login。
#
# 推荐工具: Clash Verge (或其他 mihomo 类代理软件)，默认监听端口 = 7897
# 设计记录: docs/03_Engineering/Nook-GIT-WORKFLOW.md § 十三
#
# Setup (仓储级别, 不影响其他项目):
#   git config --local http.proxy  http://127.0.0.1:7897
#   git config --local https.proxy http://127.0.0.1:7897
#
# Verify (预期 HTTP 200 in 0.2..3.0s):
#   curl -x http://127.0.0.1:7897 -s -o /dev/null #        -w 'github via proxy: HTTP %{http_code} | time %{time_total}s
' #        --max-time 15 https://github.com
#
# ⚠️ 注意:
#   - GitHub Actions CI 走云 runner, 不需代理
#   - Cloudflare Pages 部署链路不依赖代理 (CF CDN 跨过 GFW)
#   - 若代理软件启用了 authentication, 用 user:pass@127.0.0.1:7897 形式
# =============================================================================

# =============================================================================
# Copy this file to `.env` and fill in the real values.
# `.env` is git-ignored — never commit real credentials.
#
# All client-side env vars MUST use the VITE_ prefix so Vite's
# `import.meta.env` exposes them at build time (see src/config/env.ts).
# =============================================================================

# --- Supabase (Required) ------------------------------------------------------
# From Supabase Dashboard → Project Settings → API
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://<your-project-ref>.supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=<your-anon-key>

# --- App Version (Required) ---------------------------------------------------
# Keep in sync with package.json "version".
# Exposed at runtime via env.appVersion for Sentry release tagging.
VITE_APP_VERSION=0.5.0

# --- Sentry (Optional — set at M3+) -------------------------------------------
# From Sentry → Project Settings → Client Keys (DSN)
# Leave empty to disable error reporting.
VITE_SENTRY_DSN=

# --- LogSnag (Optional) -------------------------------------------------------
# From LogSnag → Workspace Settings → API Tokens
# Leave empty to disable structured event tracking.
VITE_LOGSNAG_TOKEN=

# --- Service Worker Background Sync (Optional — production only) --------------
# Set to "true" (or "1") in Cloudflare Pages production env to enable
# Workbox background sync for offline message replay.
# Defaults to false (SW disabled) in dev to avoid HMR interference.
VITE_ENABLE_SW=false
